\par 2. }{\i\fs28 C\'abng tr\'d7nh \'ae\'ad\'eang b\'e9}{\fs28  g\'e5m \'ae\'ad\'eang b\'e9, n\'aci d\'f5ng xe, \'ae\'e7 xe tr\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eang, h\'d6 th\'e8ng tho\'b8t n\'ad\'edc, \'ae\'ccn t\'ddn hi\'d6u, c\'e4c ti\'aau, bi\'d3n b\'b8o hi\'d6u, d\'b6i ph
