\par 8. }{\i\fs28 \'a7\'ad\'eang ph\'e8}{\fs28   l\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eang b\'e9 trong \'ae\'ab th\'de g\'e5m l\'dfng \'ae\'ad\'eang v\'b5 h\'cc ph\'e8.
\par 9. }{\i\fs28 D\'b6i ph\'a9n c\'b8ch}{\fs28  l\'b5 b\'e9 ph\'cbn c\'f1a \'ae\'ad\'eang \'ae\'d3 ph\'a9n chia m\'c6t \'ae\'ad\'eang th\'b5nh hai chi\'d2u xe ch\'b9y ri\'aang bi\'d6t ho\'c6c \'ae\'d3 ph\'a9n chia ph\'c7n \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'f1a xe c\'ac gi\'ed
