\par 10. }{\i\fs28 \'a7\'ad\'eang cao t\'e8c}{\fs28  l\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eang ch\'d8 d\'b5nh cho xe c\'ac gi\'edi ch\'b9y v\'edi t\'e8c \'ae\'e9 cao, c\'e3 d\'b6i ph\'a9n c\'b8ch chia \'ae\'ad\'eang cho xe ch\'b9y theo hai chi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eec nhau ri\'aang bi\'d6
