\par 11. }{\i\fs28 B\'b6o tr\'d7 \'ae\'ad\'eang b\'e9}{\fs28  l\'b5 th\'f9c hi\'d6n c\'b8c c\'abng vi\'d6c b\'b6o d\'ad\'ecng v\'b5 s\'f6a ch\'f7a nh\'bbm duy tr\'d7 ti\'aau chu\'c8n k\'fc thu\'cbt c\'f1a \'ae\'ad\'eang \'aeang khai th\'b8c.
\par {\*\bkmkstart _Hlt513017180}{\*\bkmkend _Hlt513017180}12. }{\i\fs28 Ph\'ad\'acng ti\'d6n giao th\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eang b\'e9}{\fs28  g\'e5m ph\'ad\'acng ti\'d6n giao th\'abng c\'ac gi\'edi \'ae\'ad\'eang b\'e9, ph\'ad\'acng ti\'d6n giao th\'abng th\'ab s
